1.Update system 
$sudo pacman -Syyu 

2.Install git
$sudo pacman -S git

3.Install libraries to compile packages
$sudo pacman -S binutils make gcc pkg-config fakeroot

4.Install basic tools for compiling code:
$sudo pacman -S base-devel

5.$git clone the repository and $run makepkg -Sri

6.If PGP signatures can not be verrified, run 
$gpg --recv-key <KEY SIGNATURE> 